Controversial man of God, Apostle Suleman has taken to social media to praise his daughter who turned 13 recently. , Popular clergyman, Apostle Johnson Suleman and founder of Omega Fire Ministries Worldwide has celebrated his daughter, Divine as she clocked 13 on Saturday. Suleman took to his twitter handle to shower praises on his daughter, describing her as pretty and bold. He prayed to God to keep her pure and great.“Happy 13th birthday to my 2nd seed, my pretty young lady and my bold girl. The one who always says it as it is without fear…I love you my daughter..God keep you pure and make you great..happy birthday DIVINE JOHNSON SULEMAN,” he tweeted. See photo below: Source